into consumer campaigns using facebook web banners google adwords newspaper advertisements and print inserts showcasing all of pepco’s programs that delivered  million impressions for the year facilitating the sale of more than  energy star certified appliances and  million energy star certified lighting products—an percent increase in bulb sales compared to the same time period in —resulting in annual savings of more than  megawatt hours encouraging customers to participate and take advantage of a wide range of energysaving programs and purchase energy star certified products appliances highefficiency cooling and heating systems as well as compact fluorescent light cfl and lightemitting diode led bulbs the energy star logo was seen in freestanding inserts newspaper ads direct mail utility bill inserts facebook ads google ads radio ads email rich media mobile ads and web banners collaborating with other maryland utilities and industry stakeholders to advance the empower maryland home performance with energy star program print this profile spotlight not into labels  just into savings related resources overview of award categories energy star awards archive home latest news introducing new automatic vacuum calibration system usd high power servo drive series new generation variable speed system with servo performance older posts » product spotlight mcs motordrive system welcome potomac electric corp is dedicated to innovation in electromechanical power technology to help you build better machines and control systems our product and services business is comprised of several groups that work closely together to provide reliable costeffective results for a wide range of industrial and military applications mechatronics systems designs builds and markets state of the art dc and ac servomotors spring electric brakes drive electronics and motion controllers and systems for industrial and military applications mechatronics also produces many fit form and function motors drives and complete control systems for a large variety of legacy equipment in many industries  mechatronics systems works closely with potomac repair services to help oem machine builders and end users address sustaining engineering and obsolescence our ability to quickly build direct replacements in small quantities is second to none oems and end users save large amounts of money by keeping older machines running potomac repair services is a major us provider of repairs remanufacturing and replacement products in the areas of electric motors servo motors drive electronics spindles slip rings and mechanical components over  years potomac has developed broad expertise in commercial and military applications always providing our customers a solution to their problem vacuum metrology systems is the world leader in the manufacture of fully automated machines for metrology vms also provides refurbishment and upgraderetrofit services that build on our extensive experience in the remanufacturing of semiconductor automation vacuum pumps our systems engineering services design and build unique costeffective automation for todays demanding rd and manufacturing environments   homedivisions mechatronics systemspotomac repair servicesvacuum metrology systemsabout uscontact usnews and eventscareers copyright   potomac electric corporation one westinghouse plaza boston ma  •      • wwwpotomacelectriccom • toll free      pepco  wikipedia pepco from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from potomac electric power company jump to navigation search not to be confused with tepco this article needs additional citations for verification please help improve this article by adding citations to reliable sources unsourced material may be challenged and removed february  learn how and when to remove this template message pepco logo of the potomac electric power company founded   years ago  area served washington dc metropolitan area products electric power number of employees  parent exelon website pepcocom the potomac electric power company pepco also known as pepco is a public utility owned by exelon that supplies electric power to the city of washington dc and to surrounding communities in maryland it has operated there since the s and was incorporated in  the companys current trademarked slogan is your life plugged in its former slogan was were connected to you by more than power lines contents  history  transmission system  mergers  energy efficient rebate programs  controversy  see also  references  external links historyedit the pepco headquarters in washington dc in may  pepco an acronym of potomac electric power company was founded in the late th century as a subsidiary of the washington traction and electric company one of the private streetcar companies in washington surplus power was then sold to other electric streetcar companies and to cable car companies so that they could convert to electricity later the power was sold to business and residential customers the public utility holding company act of  forced the north american company the holding company to divest itself of either their streetcar operations or their power generating utility as power generation was far more profitable north american choose to divest itself of the transport entity in  the company was reorganized and became a unit of pepco holdings inc transmission systemedit pepcos bulk transmission system consists of transmission lines operating at  kv kv  kv and  kv pepco has interconnections with potomac edison kv kv baltimore gas and electric kv kv kv and dominion virginia power kv kv mergersedit in april  pepco holdings inc phi washington dcbased parent company of atlantic city electric delmarva power and pepco announced a  billion merger with exelon a chicagobased utility company a december   article in the washington post highlighted opposition by the public to the merger with exelon arguing that it would not be in the best interest of consumers that it was likely to result in higher prices to district of columbia pepco customers and even worse reliability the merger was rejected by the district of columbia public service commission in august  though it was approved by other federal and state regulators on march   the commission finally approved the merger the merger with exelon was completed on that same day energy efficient rebate programsedit from  to  pepco offered rebate programs for residential and commercial customers looking to save energy by upgrading to energy efficient equipment and systems incentives helped to offset the initial capital cost of upgrading equipment controversyedit an investigation by the washington post in  faulted pepco for poor reliability the report noted that the companys performance had slipped since  comparing poorly to other major utilities in the frequency and duration of power outages thousands of people lost power for as many as five days after only  inches of heavy wet snow in  business insider named the company first on its list of the  most hated companies in america based on its american customer satisfaction index rating during the severe june   derecho more than half of the customers in montgomery county maryland lost electric power restoration rates severely lagged behind those of neighboring power companies that were equally impacted by the stormcitation needed pepco was unable to restore power for thousands of customers for a week in nearby fairfax county virginia dominion power restored power to most customers within  hourscitation needed in the june  derecho over  pepco customers lost power and some were not restored for  days pepco charged customers a surcharge for the time they were without power and their meters were not running an administrative fee amounting to  per customer see alsoedit investorowned utility referencesedit  httpwwwpepcocomwelcomenewsreleasesarchivesarticleaspxcid  about us  pepco pepco  retrieved    north american co v securities and exchange commission 